name: .JBX File Extension
summary: Learn about .JBX files and view a list of programs that open them.

instructions: JBX files can be opened in Microsoft Play It!, which is included with Microsoft Plus! for Kids!. Because Plus! for Kids! is discontinued and was intended to be used with Windows 95, you may have trouble installing it in newer versions of Windows.
